### HeYuanERP API Smoke Tests (run sequentially)

@base = http://localhost:5180
@json = application/json

### 1) Login (admin / CHANGE_ME)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "loginId": "admin",
  "password": "CHANGE_ME"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token); %}

### 2) Accounts (protected)
GET {{base}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) Payments - list
GET {{base}}/api/payments?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Payments - create (multipart)
